Press Release – BDS Receives Contract for Global Data Center Security Deployment of RONIN




 


 
				Broadband Discovery Systems, Inc. announced today that it has recently received a multi-million dollar contract for the design, engineering, and global deployment of the RONIN Threat Detection System for a leading Data Center client in the United States.  The RONIN systems will be deployed within the Data Centers to help streamline individual’s entry and exit processing of the areas within the data center where storage media is not permitted. The RONIN systems will be deployed over the next several months. 				Read More






RONIN Has Taken Flight Storming Beaches and Finding Mines with the US Navy




 


 
				“This technology will help Sailors and Marines who are approaching a beachfront to rapidly clear, or at least determine the location of, mines or other hazards that are in their way,” said ONR Command Master Chief Matt Matteson. “It could potentially save a lot of lives.”				Read More






