The RONIN Threat Detection System creates a physical security gate that spatially locates ferromagnetic items of interest such as guns, knives, shrapnel, or physical storage media on people as they pass through it. Deployed by the military now commercially ready with unmatched throughput rate, specific signature detection and covert deployments. 





